data.value: //Check if there is a hatchet in hand and equip one if any in pack. if not findobject 'lefthand' if @findtype 0xf43 'any' 'backpack' equipitem 'found' 2 else sysmsg 'You have run out of hatchets!' 24 endif endif //While there is still wood to cut, cut wood while not @injournal 'enough wood' useobject 'lefthand' waitfortarget 2500 targettileoffset 0 -1 0 pause 3050 //Check if there is still a hatchet equipped, in case it broke get another if not findobject 'lefthand' if @findtype 0xf43 'any' 'backpack' equipitem 'found' 2 else sysmsg 'You have run out of hatchets!' 24 endif endif endwhile @clearjournal //Cut logs into boards. if @findtype '0x1bdd' 'any' 'backpack' useobject 'lefthand' waitfortarget 15000 target 'found' endif stop
